'''Ryger Rivers''' is a minor character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Bryan McCaugherty]] and only appears in &quot;[[Baelor]].&quot; Ryger Rivers is a [[Bastards|bastard]] son of Lord [[Walder Frey]], the head of [[House Frey]] and [[Lord of the Crossing]].
